      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-700 mb-2">Microsoft Office 2021 Direct Downloads</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Choose your version and language to download original Office 2021 ISO or setup files directly from Microsoft.</p>
